{
  "stem": "26699.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was disappointed, for instance, that in the army, I wasn't considered for any single [INAUDIBLE] in spite of being trained in engineers corps, which is one of the dangerous military professions, dealing with mines and landmines and other installations.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was used only as a guard at a kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't say that it's not important to be  a guard there, but I saw that they didn't give me the right recognition when I arrived in Israel.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was also quite unhappy in my work there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I couldn't get satisfaction in my work and what I was doing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had in the past in Romania was involved in large projects, which were a professional challenge for me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was always a challenger.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I found that this possibilities of large, industrial projects for which I learned so many years, and I practiced, and I dedicated my best years, I find here in South Africa better opportunity.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My life I would say was a happy life here all these years with the exception of some tragic events. 10 years after we arrived here my wife, Lillianna, who was a tower of strength and who was an addict bodybuilder, going to gym five times a week, and all of a sudden she developed lung cancer without any sort of signs, warning signs before.",
      "word_count": 65
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had just returned from holiday in Europe, happy return, nothing happened to her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all of a sudden she developed this lung cancer, and in six months time she was dead.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was very, very depressed for a long time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then meeting through friends Anita, I remarried after three years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually I managed to get familiar with the South African lifestyle.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
